				\begin{document}$$\vec{E}, \vec{H}$$\end{document}) are calculated with Maxwell’s equations solver in time domain at each point on the 3D simulation grid.Fig. 2
Si-NW geometry (not to the scale) modeled in this study. a Dimensions of the nanowire, c-Si slab and oxide layer, b materials and illumination area along with direction and polarization and c simulation area showing different monitors, such as source, absorption and generation rate calculation
